Havoc and Demolition are going to be in the Iron Fist soon, or at 
least most of Havoc will.

::Havoc::

Havoc, Demolition, and the pod float into the cargo bay on the Iron 
Fist, the hatch closing behind them. Havoc's head, having been 
removed by Angel Prime, remains outside the base.

Missiles and laser shots are fired at Angel Prime under the water.
